Looking at this and Deep Cut's AOTY lists makes me feel I'd been sleeping for the last five years and have just woken up to this chaotic, messy musical landscape.
I've heard some great music this year, and most of it is on neither of these lists.
I truly don't know what I'm doing here to be honest.
